Class Packet

java.lang.Object
gui.Packet
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class Packet extends Object implements Serializable
Packet is class where all captured packets are saved as object. Objects can be saved as binary.

1.0

    • Packet

      public Packet(String type, String source, String destination, String header, String payload, int length, String hex, String ascii)
      Generate Packet object for IPv4 or IPv6 packet
      Parameters:
      type - packet type such as DNS or IPv6
      source - source IP address
      destination - destination IP address
      header - packet header
      payload - packet
      length - packet length / size
      hex - payload hex stream. Can be ""6
      ascii - hex stream translated to ascii / readable. Can be ""
